OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776715554
OL,3,CIran threatens to retaliate after US
OL,4,Cseizure of Iranian-flagged tanker
OL,6,FTehran has threatened to retaliate
OL,7,Fafter the seizure of an Iranian-
OL,8,Fflagged tanker by US forces in the
OL,9,FGulf of Oman on Sunday, saying it was
OL,10,Fa violation of the ceasefire and an
OL,11,Fact of "maritime piracy".
OL,13,FThe seizure of the cargo vessel casts
OL,14,Fa shadow over another round of talks
OL,15,Fin Pakistan between the US and Iran
OL,16,Faimed at extending the fragile
OL,17,Fceasefire, due to end on Wednesday.
OL,26,@sD@HOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
