PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776715554
OL,3,CIran threatens to retaliate after US
OL,4,Cseizure of Iranian-flagged tanker
OL,6,FUS Vice President JD Vance and top US
OL,7,Fofficials will travel to Pakistan for
OL,8,Fanother round of talks, but Iran has
OL,9,Fnot publicly confirmed it will send a
OL,10,Fdelegation to the talks. Some Iranian
OL,11,Fstate media outlets have suggested
OL,12,Fthat Tehran will not be at the table.
OL,14,FSeveral hurdles still need to be
OL,15,Fresolved in negotiations between the
OL,16,FUS and Iran to bring the war to an
OL,17,Fend, particularly over Iran's uranium
OL,18,Fstockpiles which have been blamed for
OL,19,Fthe first round of talks ending
OL,20,Fwithout an agreement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
