OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776715554
OL,3,CIran threatens to retaliate after US
OL,4,Cseizure of Iranian-flagged tanker
OL,6,FIranian President Masoud Pezeshkian
OL,7,Faccused the US of bullying and
OL,8,Funreasonable behaviour during previous
OL,9,Fnegotiations and during the ceasefire,
OL,10,FIranian state media reported. He
OL,11,Freportedly said that Iranian officials
OL,12,Fwere increasingly suspicious about the
OL,13,Fseriousness of the United States and
OL,14,Fthe possibility that it would repeat
OL,15,Fprevious patterns and "betray
OL,16,Fdiplomacy".
OL,18,FPresident Donald Trump said the US is
OL,19,Foffering a "very fair and reasonable
OL,20,Fdeal," but also warns he'll "do what
OL,21,Fneeds to be done" if it is rejected.
