OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776715554
OL,3,CIran threatens to retaliate after US
OL,4,Cseizure of Iranian-flagged tanker
OL,6,FThe US forcibly took the cargo ship on
OL,7,FSunday, as it tried to get around a
OL,8,Fnaval blockade near the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz on Sunday.
OL,11,FIn a post on social media, the US
OL,12,Fpresident said the ship was warned by
OL,13,Fa US Navy guided missile destroyer in
OL,14,Fthe Gulf of Oman to stop, but it did
OL,15,Fnot.
OL,17,FThe United States says it fired on the
OL,18,Fship and seized it because it had
OL,19,Fcrossed the blockade line after
OL,20,Fignoring multiple warnings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
