OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776715554
OL,3,CIran threatens to retaliate after US
OL,4,Cseizure of Iranian-flagged tanker
OL,6,FUS Central Command released a message
OL,7,Fsent by a US Mariner to the Iranian-
OL,8,Fflagged tanker in a video posted on X,
OL,9,Fsaying it shows the moments before the
OL,10,FUS seized Touska for crossing the U.S.-
OL,11,Fimposed blockade line in the Gulf of
OL,12,FOman.
OL,14,F"Motor vessel Touska, Motor vessel
OL,15,FTouska. Vacate your engine room.
OL,16,FVacate your engine room. We are about
OL,17,Fto subject you to disabling fire," can
OL,18,Fbe heard in the video. Later, three
OL,19,Frounds are fired, leaving smoke in
OL,20,Ftheir wake.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
