OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776715554
OL,3,CIran threatens to retaliate after US
OL,4,Cseizure of Iranian-flagged tanker
OL,6,FCENTCOM said the vessel's engine room
OL,7,Fwas targeted before forces seized the
OL,8,Fship. It said Touska was headed to the
OL,9,FIranian port of Bandar Abbas and
OL,10,Fignored multiple US warnings over six
OL,11,Fhours to evacuate the engine room. The
OL,12,FUSS Spruance then fired, after which
OL,13,FMarines boarded and took hold of the
OL,14,Fship.
OL,16,F"American forces acted in a
OL,17,Fdeliberate, professional, and
OL,18,Fproportional manner to ensure
OL,19,Fcompliance," it wrote on X.
